channel.title: Can't log into Czar v5
channel.description:
I downloaded the cleaned Czar V5 source and am using a regular 317 Client I found. Whenever I attempt to play. It logs me in. Saves my character. Logs me out. Why is that?
[code]Rocket Fish is signing onto server. game saved for player Rocket Fish[/code] it'll say that in my initialize.bat and then just log me out. Is this because it's the cleaned version? If so, is there a quick fix to this so I can start coding?
